{"word":"G5453 - φύω - phýō - foo'-o - Spring","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">foo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spring</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வளர், முளை"},{"paragraph":"1. to beget, bring forth, produce"},{"paragraph":"2. to shoot forth, spring up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; probably originally to &ldquo;puff&rdquo; or <i>blow</i>, that is, to <i>swell</i> up; but only used in the implied sense, to <i>germinate</i> or <i>grow</i> (<i>sprout</i>, <i>produce</i>), literally or figuratively: - spring (up).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}